{
  "version": 1,
  "note": [
    "SINGLE authoritative inventory of every metric series the §18 dashboards and",
    "§20.1 alert rules are allowed to reference (issue #156). This REPLACES the old",
    "hand-maintained REAL_BASE set and the permissive `^otelcol_` prefix allowlist in",
    "validate_dashboards.py — there is now exactly one list, not two.",
    "",
    "`emitted` is the OTLP instruments our own Go code registers. It is kept honest",
    "against the instrumentation by deploy/obs/inventory_drift_test.py, which parses",
    "the instrument constructors in services/core/internal and FAILS the gate if this",
    "file drifts from the code — so adding/removing an instrument forces a matching",
    "edit here. FOLLOW-UP (scoped, issue #156): replace this checked-in artifact with a",
    "codegen step that emits it directly from the Go/Python instrument registry (`task",
    "obs:inventory`), so the drift guard becomes a build step rather than a test.",
    "",
    "`collector_internal` is the OpenTelemetry Collector's OWN self-telemetry",
    "(otelcol_*): series we do not emit but scrape via the otel-collector-internal job.",
    "They are enumerated EXPLICITLY (not by prefix) so a typo like",
    "`otelcol_metric_that_does_not_exist` fails the gate.",
    "",
    "Prometheus names: OTLP `.`->`_` only (collector add_metric_suffixes:false, no",
    "`_total`/`_seconds`). Histograms expand to _bucket/_sum/_count."
  ],
  "prometheus_naming": {
    "add_metric_suffixes": false,
    "histogram_suffixes": ["_bucket", "_sum", "_count"]
  },
  "emitted": {
    "execution.write_attempts": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "domain",
      "source": "internal/execution/telemetry.go"
    },
    "execution.dedup_hits": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "domain",
      "source": "internal/execution/telemetry.go"
    },
    "execution.gate_blocks": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "domain",
      "source": "internal/execution/telemetry.go"
    },
    "execution.pending_reconciliation": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "domain",
      "source": "internal/execution/telemetry.go"
    },
    "execution.recommend_only": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "domain",
      "source": "internal/execution/telemetry.go"
    },
    "execution.terminal_results": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "domain",
      "source": "internal/execution/telemetry.go"
    },
    "execution.audit_write_failures": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "domain",
      "source": "internal/execution/telemetry.go"
    },
    "execution.enablement_denied": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "domain",
      "source": "internal/execution/telemetry.go"
    },
    "execution.crash_recoveries": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "domain",
      "source": "internal/execution/telemetry.go"
    },
    "execution.pending_reconciliation_current": {
      "type": "gauge",
      "family": "domain",
      "source": "internal/execution/reconciliation_backlog.go"
    },
    "execution.pending_reconciliation_oldest_age_seconds": {
      "type": "gauge",
      "family": "domain",
      "source": "internal/execution/reconciliation_backlog.go"
    },
    "analytics.events": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "analytics",
      "source": "internal/analytics/telemetry.go"
    },
    "analytics.cost_minor_units": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "analytics",
      "source": "internal/analytics/telemetry.go"
    },
    "analytics.tenant_rejections": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "analytics",
      "source": "internal/analytics/telemetry.go"
    },
    "analytics.entity_rejections": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "analytics",
      "source": "internal/analytics/telemetry.go"
    },
    "http.server.request.duration": {
      "type": "histogram",
      "family": "red",
      "source": "internal/httpapi/telemetry.go"
    },
    "connector.sync_failure_streak": {
      "type": "gauge",
      "family": "domain",
      "source": "internal/catalog/telemetry.go"
    },
    "connector.sync_results": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "domain",
      "source": "internal/catalog/telemetry.go"
    },
    "connector.sync_streak_seed_bound_exhausted": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "domain",
      "source": "internal/catalog/telemetry.go"
    },
    "connector.catalog_sync_initiations": {
      "type": "counter",
      "family": "domain",
